<h1>Bots That Yell</h1>
<div class="text">
	<%= ENV['URL']%> is an ActivityPub server that can provide you with a bot that yells. Simply follow any single character @<%= ENV['URL'] %> (i.e. <%= link_to "@x@#{ENV['URL']}", 'letters/x' %> or <%= link_to "@🐺@#{ENV['URL']}", 'letters/🐺' %>), you'll receive a new exclamation of that character every two hours. Forever, if you so desire!
</div>
<div class="text">
	<%= form_with url: "/letters", method: :post do |form| %>
		<%= form.label :query, "Search for any character to see our offerings:" %><br>
		<%= form.text_field :query, size: 1, maxlength: 1 %>
		<%= form.submit "Search" %>
	<% end %>
</div>

<div class="text">
	<%= ENV['URL'] %> is made by <a href="https://akirchner.website">Alexa Kirchner</a>.
</div>